item.title: Deep Blue Something - Breakfast At Tiffany's
item.description:
Ukulele play along Breakfast At Tiffany's - Deep Blue Something
Using the chords: A D G
Suggested Strum Patterns: D DU U DU
Play D DU U DU for the D chord then D D for the G chord and U DU for the A chord - this is a slow pattern but try faster, more complex patterns if you like ;-)
This video is meant for educational purposes.
No copyright infringement intended
